17 Sec. 9. 1. An operator shall inspect an inflatable device,
18 before allowing any person to use the inflatable device, to ensure
19 all original labels attached to the inflatable device by the
20 manufacturer remain attached and are legible. If any label
21 attached by the manufacturer is missing, use of the inflatable
22 device must be permanently discontinued and the inflatable device
